com.paypal.selion.grid.servlets.transfer

Interface ManagedArtifact

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultManagedArtifact

    public interface ManagedArtifact
    ManagedArtifact represents a basic artifact successfully saved to SeLion grid by an HTTP POST method call.
